Classes:
Juggernaut: Slow weapons gain x damage
Rogue: Crits apply stacking bleed
Necromancer: Deal damage on death
Berserker: Damage increases as HP gets lower
Paladin: Healing effects deal damage

Weaknesses: Revive time increased, non-crits deal reduced damage, healing reduced, attack speed reduced

Archetypes
Each archetype has different affinities for weapons. Some weapons are going to be majorly reduced on certain archetypes

Modifier part
One part simply amplifies and reduces the affects of other parts
